<br>
We are both Erudite mages and are currently killing large/giant bats, rabid wolves and other stuff in Qeynos hills.  We don't want to go into Blackburrow neither of us really like dungeons and trains.<br>
<br>
My questions are:<br>
1. Where should we go to hunt?<br>
2. And once there what should we be looking to kill?<br>
<br>
I have heard that Misty thicket is good.<br>
Is there anyplace else that is a little closer, maybe in the Karanas or in Everfrost? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#333333>(10/3/00 2:54:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm38.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 2 mages lvl 6 - where to hunt and what?</span><hr size=1> those beggars and skeletons and maybe thugs in qeynos sewer. No train there.<br>
