<br>
Hunt wisps.  Find one that is all alone (they'll gang up on you) and pull it to the beach, close to the water. That way, you dont have to worry about them ganging up on you.<br>
<br>
Take the lightstones and greater lightstones that you get and head over to North Karana. There, go to the gypsi camp and give the stones to a merchant named Mrysia (or something like that).<br>
<br>
Lightstones will give you a wizard research book that is worth around 8 silver.<br>
<br>
Greater Lightstones will give you a wizard reseach container-type thing.  Since this is a container, you wont be able to put it in a bag.  The annoyance is well worth the 8pp (or more) that you'll get for it though.<br>
<br>
